replies.author: a1294790523
replies.txt_content:
# There is insufficient memory for the Java Runtime Environment to continue.
# Native memory allocation (mmap) failed to map 1224736768 bytes for Failed to commit area from 0x0000000654000000 to 0x000000069d000000 of length 1224736768.-Xmn128m -Xmx8192m
你设置的内存超出了系统能分配的内存上限，请降低分配的内存，一般4G（4096M）就可以了，没必要分配这么多
